This is the theme for the [[[ad-astra-per-aspera-hub|Ad Astra Per Aspera]]] canon!

To use it, put the following syntax at the very top of your article.
~~~~
> @@[[include theme:ad-astra]]@@

There are six quoteblock colors: black (default), blue, pink, gold, purple and gray. Use them with the following code:

[[div class="blue"]]
> @@[[div class="blue"]]@@
[[/div]]
[[div class="pink"]]
