If using the {{@@[[div class="blockquote"]]@@}} feature of Sigma-9, you can change the color of the blockquote by adding the color as a class after blockquote (i.e. {{@@[[div class="blockquote blue"]]@@}}).

You can define [[span class="h-span"]]highlighted (colored and bold) text[[/span]] with {{@@[[span class="h-span"]]@@}}. It is suggested that you use this for [[span class="h-span"]]Item #:[[/span]], [[span class="h-span"]]Object Class:[[/span]], [[span class="h-span"]]Description[[/span]], etc.

